{"tid":2112181,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「天鴿」襲港期間執勤遭塌樹壓傷 交通警入稟控告警務處處長索償","createTime":"2020-07-17T06:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T10:13:20.000Z","uid":240362,"like":443,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"a41c1d50f7640da21dcf2d3958d6654ba7cfb2be","tid":2112181,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T06:08:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200717/P4Y3XCQ3T54KACGDCZ4UYUNUUY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200717%2FP4Y3XCQ3T54KACGDCZ4UYUNUUY%2F&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpQu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=d37ae177\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200717%2FP4Y3XCQ3T54KACGDCZ4UYUNUUY%2F&h=fee44663\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200717/P4Y3XCQ3T54KACGDCZ4UYUNUUY/</a><br />\n<br />\n強颱風「天鴿」2017年8月襲港，造成狂風暴雨，天文台更懸掛10號風球，全港多區塌樹。兩名東九龍交通部警員處理塌樹期間，遭倒下的樹幹壓傷，其中一人重傷，一度留醫深切治療部。其中一名受傷警昨日入稟高等法院，控告警務處處長，指事故是源於處方疏忽所致，要求賠償。惟入稟狀未有提及傷患詳情或索償金額。"},{"pid":"3e2ce3281aaf3aefaeb6679e9b86289fb9ffce5b","tid":2112181,"uid":151313,"like":284,"dislike":1,"score":283,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T06:09:06.000Z","msg":"犯左國安法啦"},{"pid":"98155bb365dbb79d0a9030e972523541e038ac27","tid":2112181,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3e2ce3281aaf3aefaeb6679e9b86289fb9ffce5b","tid":2112181,"uid":151313,"like":284,"dislike":1,"score":283,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T06:09:06.000Z","msg":"犯左國安法啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T06:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b7014dc70faaf51f67802878844bacadc1a4888","tid":2112181,"uid":194298,"like":156,"dislike":1,"score":155,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T06:10:27.000Z","msg":"為特區政府帶來仇恨?<img src=\"/assets